00:32:07.270 --> 00:32:08.650
6 na musikero, 2 attendant,

00:32:08.650 --> 00:32:09.350
2 matrona para i-escort ang nobya,

00:32:09.350 --> 00:32:10.070
2 matrona na tumanggap sa kanya,

00:32:10.070 --> 00:32:10.750
at 12 mesa para sa piging.

00:32:10.750 --> 00:32:11.720
Walang mawawala.

00:32:11.720 --> 00:32:12.790
Huwag mong guluhin ito para sa akin.

00:32:12.790 --> 00:32:13.790
Panigurado, Sir.

