00:41:19.680 --> 00:41:21.220
Pero kailangan mo siyang tanungin.

00:41:22.360 --> 00:41:24.290
Kahit gaano ka pa kagusto ng isang babae,

00:41:24.550 --> 00:41:25.880
kung hindi ka man lang makapagbigay
ng disenteng damit-pangkasal

00:41:25.880 --> 00:41:26.950
para maisuot niya,

00:41:27.510 --> 00:41:30.110
at hindi man lang siya nagrereklamo,
dapat may mali.

00:41:30.110 --> 00:41:31.920
